{"tid":1501671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨近中秋 唔知大家細細個有冇煲蠟？","createTime":"2019-08-24T12:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:54:36.000Z","uid":33308,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4f4c001c50eba3385f209340a4213ebaf1b097","tid":1501671,"uid":33308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"細路仔個陣總係追求刺激<br />\n鐘意係月餅罐入面點下蠟燭<br />\n之後比朋友教路話唔過癮<br />\n攞<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">火柴</span>出黎玩<br />\n夾住係火柴盒同姆指之間彈出去<br />\n就變成識著<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span>既手裡劍啦！<br />\n仲唔夠喉？<br />\n我地有時會買幾蚊個既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打火機</span></strong><br />\n做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">爆裂彈</span></span><br />\n放落著左火既月餅盒度<br />\n個下火光幾震撼呀 成個小型核爆咁<br />\n唔知大家細個又有做咩頑皮野呢？<br />\n利申：最近發左個怪夢 見到一個又一個人射盲左<br />\n覺得好憤怒 醒左就要減下壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268fd58aa9fbe868e48d993f7af397913236aec3","tid":1501671,"uid":227275,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/76Arbg6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76Arbg6.gif&h=52c53038&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"869c9ebb03ad130f4a85b2e3cf9df26b3aeb5d35","tid":1501671,"uid":33308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808e64304314e0f7d387f7442d7f879af950f483","tid":1501671,"uid":33308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d977384e48f2e3b25a00c8b9b8271412e390e0d5","tid":1501671,"uid":33308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T12:17:18.000Z","msg":"Bu